titlestmt.titleproper: Rockefeller (John D., Sr.) papers, Financial Material, Vouchers, Subseries FV
A Guide to the John D. Rockefeller, Sr. papers, Financial Material, Vouchers, Subseries FV FA262

profiledesc.creation: This finding aid was produced using ArchivesSpace on 2020-12-16 05:16:12 -0500.

did.unittitle: John D. Rockefeller, Sr. papers, Financial Material, Vouchers, Subseries FV

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: The John D. Rockefeller papers were given to the Rockefeller Archive Center by the Rockefeller Brothers in 1976.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Open for research. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of RAC.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Subseries FV primarily contains financial vouchers documenting the activities of John D. Rockefeller and John D. Rockefeller Jr. in the late 19th and early 20th century.
